---
id: haiti-earthquake
layout: page
---
section[class="row flex-fill"]
  div[class="col-12 mx-auto haiti-earthquake-wrapper"]
    div[class="row"]
      div[class="col-12"]
        div[class="row mx-auto haiti-earthquake-details-wrapper"]
          div[class="col-12 title"]
            span
              |Haiti 2010 Earthquake
            span
              |Disaster Proposal
          div[class="col-12 cta"]
            = data.haitiearthquake.cta

          div[class="col-12 proposal"]
            |Our proposal included:
          div[class="col-12 our-proposal"]
            ul
              - data.haitiearthquake.proposals.us.sort_by { |k| k["id"] }.each_with_index do |proposal, index|
                li
                  = proposal.description

          div[class="col-12 proposal"]
            |Advanced Building Technology mobilized these Haiti Relief Partners:
          div[class="col-12 partner-proposal"]
            ul
              - data.haitiearthquake.proposals.partners.sort_by { |k| k["id"] }.each_with_index do |proposal, index|
                li
                  = proposal.description

          div[class="col-12"]
            div[class="row video-wrapper"]
              div[class="col-12 title"]
                |ABT SELECTED TEMO INC. AS ONE OF OUR PARTNERS FOR THE 2010 HAITI EARTHQUAKE DISASTER RELIEF PROJECT. THE VIDEO WAS INCLUDED IN OUR PRESENTATION.
              div[class="col-12"]
                div[class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9"]
                  iframe[class="embed-responsive-item" src="#{data.haitiearthquake.video.url}?rel=0" allowfullscreen title="#{data.haitiearthquake.video.description}" alt="#{data.haitiearthquake.video.tags}"]
              div[class="col-12"]
                = data.haitiearthquake.video.details
